<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: deadlife capsule -->
  <Bullet_Shell_Deadlife.label>死灵弹</Bullet_Shell_Deadlife.label>
  
  <!-- EN: ghoul resurrection serum -->
  <GhoulResurrectionSerum.label>食尸鬼复活血清</GhoulResurrectionSerum.label>
  <!-- EN: A capsule of thick grey fluid containing a mixture of deadlife dust and advanced biochemicals. Inject it into the corpse of a ghoul to return them to life. The resurrection process takes several hours. -->
  <GhoulResurrectionSerum.description>装有灰色流体的胶囊，混合了死灵尘与高级生化药剂。注射进食尸鬼的尸体后，血清会令其死而复生。复活过程需要数个小时。</GhoulResurrectionSerum.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <GhoulResurrectionSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用{0_label}</GhoulResurrectionSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: juggernaut serum -->
  <JuggernautSerum.label>强力血清</JuggernautSerum.label>
  <!-- EN: A syringe of opaque milky-yellow liquid that increases the user's strength and speed, and allows them to recover from injuries faster. The serum is injected into the user's musculature, where it adds energy to various metabolic processes. However, the unstable substance also psychically influences the mind, provoking unsettling thoughts and severely reducing the user's mood. -->
  <JuggernautSerum.description>装有不透明乳黄色流体的注射针剂，能够提升使用者的速度和力量，并让其伤口愈合更快。注射进肌肉后，血清会为使用者的各种代谢过程提供能量。然而这种不稳定的物质也会对使用者的心智精神造成影响，令其紧张不安、情绪低落。</JuggernautSerum.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <JuggernautSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用{0_label}</JuggernautSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  <!-- EN: Ingest {0} -->
  <JuggernautSerum.ingestible.ingestCommandString>注射{0}</JuggernautSerum.ingestible.ingestCommandString>
  <!-- EN: Ingesting {0}. -->
  <JuggernautSerum.ingestible.ingestReportString>注射{0}。</JuggernautSerum.ingestible.ingestReportString>
  
  <!-- EN: metalblood serum -->
  <MetalbloodSerum.label>钢血血清</MetalbloodSerum.label>
  <!-- EN: A syringe full of rust-colored liquid that constantly hardens and liquifies. When injected into the bloodstream, the metalblood substance can harden the flesh when it anticipates a blow, making the user more resistant to damage. However, the bioferrite-based chemistry of this serum also makes the user particularly vulnerable to fire. -->
  <MetalbloodSerum.description>装有铁锈色流体的注射针剂，其中的药剂不断地在液态与固态间往复变化。注射进血液后，这种钢血物质能够使肉体在受到冲击前迅速硬化，让使用者抵御更多伤害。然而，这种基于活铁的化学物质也让使用者面对火焰时格外脆弱。</MetalbloodSerum.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <MetalbloodSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用{0_label}</MetalbloodSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  <!-- EN: Ingest {0} -->
  <MetalbloodSerum.ingestible.ingestCommandString>注射{0}</MetalbloodSerum.ingestible.ingestCommandString>
  <!-- EN: Ingesting {0}. -->
  <MetalbloodSerum.ingestible.ingestReportString>注射{0}。</MetalbloodSerum.ingestible.ingestReportString>
  
  <!-- EN: mind-numb serum -->
  <MindNumbSerum.label>思滞血清</MindNumbSerum.label>
  <!-- EN: A syringe of clear, viscous fluid. Injected near the brainstem, it deadens the mind, rendering the user unable to feel the highs and lows of human emotion. This temporarily prevents them from having mental breaks and inspirations. -->
  <MindNumbSerum.description>装有澄清黏性流体的注射针剂。向脑干附近注射后能够使被使用者思维停滞、不再感受到人情冷暖。这将暂时阻止此人发生精神崩溃或是激发灵感。</MindNumbSerum.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <MindNumbSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用{0_label}</MindNumbSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
  <!-- EN: Ingest {0} -->
  <MindNumbSerum.ingestible.ingestCommandString>注射{0}</MindNumbSerum.ingestible.ingestCommandString>
  <!-- EN: Ingesting {0}. -->
  <MindNumbSerum.ingestible.ingestReportString>注射{0}。</MindNumbSerum.ingestible.ingestReportString>
  
  <!-- EN: deadlife shell -->
  <Shell_Deadlife.label>死灵弹</Shell_Deadlife.label>
  <!-- EN: An artillery shell packed with a dust-like substance that, after exploding into a cloud, will settle on nearby human and animal corpses and raise them as shamblers. The shamblers will only attack your enemies.\n\nThis can be fired from mortars or installed as a trap. Explodes when damaged. -->
  <Shell_Deadlife.description>装填了大量死灵尘的炮弹。炮弹发射后，会插入地面一段时间并持续释放死灵尘，能够将周围的人类及动物尸体转变为蹒跚怪。这些蹒跚怪只会攻击你的敌人。可以用迫击炮发射或者安装成一个陷阱。受损后爆炸。</Shell_Deadlife.description>
  
  <!-- EN: deadlife capsule -->
  <Shell_Deadlife_Releasing.label>死灵弹</Shell_Deadlife_Releasing.label>
  
  <!-- EN: voidsight serum -->
  <VoidsightSerum.label>虚空视界血清</VoidsightSerum.label>
  <!-- EN: A capsule of oily black fluid that squirms endlessly inside the glass. When injected into the eye, it suppresses the inhibitory neurons that keep perception focused on the real world, thus lifting dark psychic phenomena into conscious perception. This increases the amount of knowledge gained when studying unnatural entities, as well as psychic sensitivity, but also impacts mood.\n\nThe effect is temporary and does not stack. -->
  <VoidsightSerum.description>黑色油状物质在针管内不断扭曲蠕动。注射进眼球后能打通虚空视界，让使用者能够感知暗黑心灵现象。调查异常实体时使用此药物可提升异象知识的获取效率，同时提高心灵敏感度，但也影响心情。\n\n此药效果是暂时的，且药效不能叠加。</VoidsightSerum.description>
  <!-- EN: Use {0_label} -->
  <VoidsightSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>使用{0_label}</VoidsightSerum.comps.CompUsable.useLabel>
